{"tid":561430,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一個半場斬65次波 廣州恒大亞冠盃出師不利","createTime":"2018-02-15T04:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T04:25:14.000Z","uid":55981,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f0dbc7ba677fe1b6bfb8a65f345fc92aeb424c10","tid":561430,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:06:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180214/57834738\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57834738&d=X8FF1IDY7L640IgtqOALI9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=bb31bcd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57834738&h=8107f83c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180214/57834738</a><br />\n<br />\n兩屆亞冠盃冠軍廣州恒大出戰亞冠分組賽首戰，只能與泰國的武里南聯打和，出師不利。賽後，第二次上任恒大主帥的簡拿華路表示，球隊下半場太多兩翼傳中。<br />\n<br />\n今季載譽歸來的簡拿華路賽後記者會表示，下半場恒大球員的專注力有所下降，令球隊經常被對手藉反擊攻門。而且，亦指出球員下半場不停用長傳急攻的方法不理想，「我特意翻看賽後統計數據，發現球隊下半場兩翼傳中高達65次，這完全中正對手下懷，對方擺出5人後防，傳中的實效不大，我們應該用更多短傳入滲。」<br />\n<br />\n同組的大阪櫻花以1:0擊敗濟洲聯，令下場作客日本的恒大有更大取分壓力。而大簡希望球員忘記今仗和局，調整心情，努力預備下星期對大阪櫻花的比賽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C4N1DANWAAEnlXE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC4N1DANWAAEnlXE.jpg&h=369f0735&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ced3ca6425e43a34892fc22025c953abf54fb58","tid":561430,"uid":5843,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/6/66/UiP6vjX.gif/revision/latest?cb=20140306063440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F6%2F66%2FUiP6vjX.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140306063440&h=1124a9d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f2d87bd2fb0a4bedcf2f9afe1b612c577d01901","tid":561430,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:22:53.000Z","msg":"大簡原來番左去教啦， 咁史高拉利去左邊"},{"pid":"026ff0ef7250c25b389f8015717779bfa53978cb","tid":561430,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f2d87bd2fb0a4bedcf2f9afe1b612c577d01901","tid":561430,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:22:53.000Z","msg":"大簡原來番左去教啦， 咁史高拉利去左邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:25:14.000Z","msg":"教返巴西"}]}